meetupData.title: India International Hospitality Expo 2024
meetupData.description: India International Hospitality Expo is all set to welcome B2B buyers from across luxury hotels, resorts, homestays, restaurants, cloud kitchens, and everyone in the hospitality and F&B space. The show has emerged as the most sought-after sourcing hub for the Hospitality and F&B industry. From CEOs to purchase heads and project management companies
